	<item>
		<title>About Us</title>
		<link>http://localhost/about/</link>
		<pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2025 12:01:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://localhost/?page_id=4</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Our Story:</strong> AquaLuxe was founded with a passion for bringing the beauty and tranquility of the aquatic world to homes and businesses. From our humble beginnings as a local farm, we have grown into an international brand recognized for our commitment to quality, sustainability, and ethical sourcing.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Our Mission:</strong> To provide the finest ornamental fish, aquatic plants, and aquarium supplies, while promoting responsible fishkeeping and environmental stewardship.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Our Values:</strong> We believe in quality, integrity, and customer satisfaction. We are dedicated to the health and well-being of our aquatic life and the satisfaction of our customers.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
